msgid ""
"ApprovalRuleForm refactored to fields=\"__all__\" with field_order, dropping "
"the unused process_config field and the redundant view fields list. Fixed a "
"KeyError on review-process create by adding keep_on_form for is_active. "
"Migrated signal imports to the horilla.db.models.signals shim and added "
"docstrings for pylint compliance."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Release 1.10: Process Builder consolidated under contrib.process with "
"approvals and reviews sub-apps. Django app labels for approvals and reviews "
"are unchanged; import paths and includes now use the contrib package layout."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Enhanced approval workflow with delete support in approval history, standard "
"HTMX modal delete flow, and inline edit enforcement for pending/rejected "
"records. Improved approval signals cleanup, review process table viewport "
"handling, and redirect behavior."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Introduced unified Process Builder combining reviews and approvals into a "
"flexible, condition-driven workflow engine with configurable approvers, "
"field-level controls, and per-app process configuration."
msgstr ""

